    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly in showroom condition! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still looks and feels brand new. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been babied since day one, this is definitely the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
