    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle has been meticulously preserved as a collector-grade example. The exterior retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating, showing zero swirl marks, dings, or road rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather still carries its original scent, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment to the ambient lighting\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all major maintenance completed ahead of schedule. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a thick binder of service records for the discerning buyer seeking absolute perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
