      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade specimen maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer, featuring an immaculate exterior profile and a pristine cabin that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically flawless and documented with precision, this unit exemplifies the pinnacle of automotive preservation. We invite serious inquiries for this distinguished example of engineering excellence.",
