      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, the valvetrain is whisper-quiet following recent shim adjustments and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains structurally flawless with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM bushings. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with zero paint correction required, while the interior demonstrates minimal bolster wear and a functional, pixel-perfect instrument cluster. A true collector-grade specimen with a documented service history.",
